“If no set-back happens, Koeman will be Barcelona’s coach next season,” Josep Maria Bartomeu has just revealed in an interview with Barcelona TV. The president has explained his pick: “We bet on Koeman because of his experience of the Barca style, and that he believes in the Barca philosophy and he was in the dream team.” READ ALSO: I want to coach Barca -Koeman Still, he has conceded the Dutchman hasn’t yet signed a contract. The Dutch coach is expected to sign a two-year deal with the Catalan club with the official confirmation imminent. 